Title: What Was Missing
Writer: Pendleton Ward (created by), Pendleton Ward, Mark Banker (story by), Patrick McHale (story by), Kent Osborne (story by), Pendleton Ward (story by), Adam Muto, Rebecca Sugar
Actors: Jeremy Shada, John DiMaggio, Hynden Walch, Olivia Olson
Plot: In order to open a magic door filled with stolen items, Finn and all his friends must perform in a band. But everyone's differing musical tastes and overall tensions make things difficult.
